description: Alex Gerrard, wife of England and Liverpool captain Steven Gerrard, is a fashion journalist in England.
Michela Quattrociocche is the wife of Italian World Cup squad hopeful Alberto Aquilani.
Rumors swirled about Chelsea player and Nigeria footballer Jon Obi Mikel's marriage to model Sandra Okagbue, but both have denied such reports.
A TV journalist in Greece, Katerina Kainourgiou has been linked to Greece national team standout Georgios Samaras. Samaras also plays for Celtic in Scotland.
Sarah Brandner has been dating German midfielder and Bayern Munich star Bastian Schweinstager since 2007.
Susana Werner, a Brazilian model and actress, is married to Brazil No. 1 Julio Cesar. The couple has two children, Cauet and Giulia.
Spanish television presenter Sara Carbonero is expecting a child with Spain and Real Madrid net-minder Iker Casillas.

description: We've seen Cristiano Ronaldo's dazzling moves on the pitch, but is it possible he and some of the other World Cup participants are using their signifcant others as muses? We might never know, but it's hard to argue that the beautiful game carries over off the pitch, as well.
